The dimensions of a basketball court and bleachers is shown. A fence is to be installed that follows the edges of the court and bleachers (except for their shared edge). The fence costs \$8.99 per foot. How much will the fence cost?

\begin{tikzpicture}[scale=0.04]
% Basketball court (main rectangle)
\draw (0,0) rectangle (105,70);
% Center circle
\draw (52.5,35) circle (8);
% Left semicircle (three-point arc area)
\draw (0,20) arc (270:90:15);
% Right semicircle
\draw (105,20) arc (-90:90:15);
% Bleachers below the court
\draw (15,0) -- (15,-15) -- (90,-15) -- (90,0);
% Dimension labels
\node at (52.5, 75) {105 ft};
\node at (112, 35) {70 ft};
\node at (7.5, -7.5) {15 ft};
\node at (52.5, -20) {75 ft};
\node at (97, -7.5) {30 ft};
\node at (100, -15) {15 ft};
\end{tikzpicture}
